<SYNC START=3121200><P Class=EGCC>
I challenged Mr West to a stiff climb...<br>
and won.
<SYNC START=3125800><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC START=3126700><P Class=EGCC>
Her legs are longer. <br>
When I reached top you'd disappeared.
<SYNC START=3130700><P Class=EGCC>&nbsp;
